    public class EntryImpl
extends EntryBaseImpl
    The extended model implementation for the Entry service. Represents a row in the "GB_Entry" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

    Helper methods and all application logic should be put in this class. Whenever methods are added, rerun ServiceBuilder to copy their definitions into the Entry interface.
